data.description: ASK YOUR AGENT ABOUT THE ADDITIONAL PERKS OF BUYING THIS HOME! Built by the renowned RAUSCH COLEMAN in the desirable Harrington Trails community. With 10-foot ceilings, 42-inch kitchen cabinets, custom backsplash, quartz counter tops, modern vinyl flooring, open-concept design, stainless steel appliances and ample counter space, this home is a knockout beyond the typical standard build. The primary suite features a generous layout, plush carpeting, an attached bath with gorgeous tile, garden tub and huge walk-in closet. Additional bedrooms are very spacious and perfect for children, guests, or a home office. Indoor utility room includes LG washer/dryer and garage comes equipped with automatic opener. Neighborhood offers many amenities including new pool, splash pad, walking trails, playground and rec center. Elementary school conveniently located in subdivision with middle school to open soon. Just 30 minutes North of downtown, easy access to major highways, including 59 and 45.
